-- Gunman Takes Hostages in Leipzig Store, Talking With Police by Telephone
-- Tony Czuczka
-- 2010-06-15T13:51:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-15/gunman-takes-hostages-in-leipzig-store-talking-with-police-by-telephone.html

          
          
             German police are talking by
telephone to a man holding an undetermined number of hostages in
a store in Leipzig, trying to persuade him to give himself up,
Uwe Voigt, a spokesman for city police, said in a phone
interview.  
          
          


  


        